{"tid":1665041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［冇人講？］李慧詩贏撚咗支國選手鍾天使 成功亞錦四連霸ㅤ明戰凱林賽爭雙冠","createTime":"2019-10-20T12:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T13:33:11.000Z","uid":48083,"like":122,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"9a08e3e5cbce0c488017c365b5abee336ea75be7","tid":1665041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"【體路韓國鎮川直擊】正在韓國鎮川舉行的 2020 亞洲場地單車錦標賽進入第四天賽事，香港隊終有第一金落袋！「牛下女車神」李慧詩（Sarah）今午（20 日）在女子爭先賽決賽清脆俐落以直落兩場 K.O. 中國的鍾天使，歷來第六次在這個項目掄元，更實現史無前例的四連霸，明日將乘勇轉戰凱林賽，力爭雙冠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQRqE2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQRqE2L.jpg&h=7f05a399&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxtXv9s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxtXv9s.jpg&h=3045778c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLbBMHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLbBMHO.jpg&h=1f419e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MJTOWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MJTOWb.jpg&h=05746c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzVfhPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzVfhPx.jpg&h=ae2c0211&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyNYfBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyNYfBd.jpg&h=75c62513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經在 2012、2015 及 2017 至 2019 年五度在亞錦賽女子爭先賽封后的 Sarah，今屆晉級過程相當輕鬆，昨日先後淘汰哈薩克及馬來西亞選手，今早於 4 強又以直落 2 場擊敗日本的小林優香。<br />\n<br />\n李慧詩下午決戰實力相當的中國名將鍾天使，兩人亦是連續三屆在亞錦爭先賽決賽碰頭，雙方第一場爭持激烈，由頭鬥到尾，狀態大勇的 Sarah 憑豐富經驗及強勁爆發力率先衝線，先拔頭籌。第二場李慧詩愈戰愈勇，全程「睇定嚟食」，最終大勝而回，直落 2:0 再挫鍾天使，第六度封后，也摘下香港隊本屆賽事第一面金牌。<br />\n<br />\n李慧詩稱霸爭先賽後，周一（21 日）在煞科日將轉戰女子凱林賽，同樣爭取這個強項的第六面亞錦賽金牌。她此前在 2013 到 2018 年內曾五度奪金，期間僅於 2015 年「斷纜」，今年 1 月亞錦賽亦因過早發力，最終「意外」不敵小林優香，屈居亞軍。<br />\n<br />\n經過四天角逐後，港隊目前累積 1 金 1 銀 2 銅獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n文、圖：三井<br />\n原刊於《體路》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/sport/韓國直擊-港隊第一金-%E1%85%A0李慧詩爭先賽亞錦四連霸%E1%85%A0明戰凱林賽爭雙冠/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%87%91-%25E1%2585%25A0%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E8%A9%A9%E7%88%AD%E5%85%88%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%9E%E9%8C%A6%E5%9B%9B%E9%80%A3%E9%9C%B8%25E1%2585%25A0%E6%98%8E%E6%88%B0%E5%87%B1%E6%9E%97%E8%B3%BD%E7%88%AD%E9%9B%99%E5%86%A0%2F&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f4aab140\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%8A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%87%91-%25E1%2585%25A0%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E8%A9%A9%E7%88%AD%E5%85%88%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%9E%E9%8C%A6%E5%9B%9B%E9%80%A3%E9%9C%B8%25E1%2585%25A0%E6%98%8E%E6%88%B0%E5%87%B1%E6%9E%97%E8%B3%BD%E7%88%AD%E9%9B%99%E5%86%A0%2F&h=0f6fe619\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/sport/韓國直擊-港隊第一金-%E1%85%A0李慧詩爭先賽亞錦四連霸%E1%85%A0明戰凱林賽爭雙冠/</a>"},{"pid":"b53db442b3031a398a80a7c41d3449c25f17948b","tid":1665041,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"有無運動撚講下第一幅圖"},{"pid":"8562cbb0231f57401d5bcc2f96e43192e4c137e1","tid":1665041,"uid":18691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"過埋今晚先 sorry 詩詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[url][/url]"},{"pid":"e5df3983917206dde4d15af611522aa615cb945a","tid":1665041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53db442b3031a398a80a7c41d3449c25f17948b","tid":1665041,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:06:42.000Z","msg":"有無運動撚講下第一幅圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"提供起動力量？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr